you or your kind.

454
00:18:14,178 --> 00:18:15,644
I thought
i made it clear.

455
00:18:15,679 --> 00:18:18,147
Yes, but i think
that jerry has...

456
00:18:18,182 --> 00:18:20,532
i think the first
order of business

457
00:18:20,567 --> 00:18:21,784
is to get you
out of here.

458
00:18:23,570 --> 00:18:24,787
Marty, marty!

459
00:18:26,690 --> 00:18:28,540
Let's get
that battering ram

460
00:18:28,575 --> 00:18:30,409
