down that door.

461
00:18:30,444 --> 00:18:33,545
You've had your chance,
stockton, remember that!

462
00:18:33,580 --> 00:18:35,414
You've had
your chance!

463
00:18:35,449 --> 00:18:37,299
Come on, marty,
come on.

