00:18:47,211 --> 00:18:49,061
those people
are our neighbors,

468
00:18:49,096 --> 00:18:49,678
our friends,

469
00:18:49,713 --> 00:18:52,181
the people
we've lived with

470
00:18:52,216 --> 00:18:54,683
and alongside
for 20 years.

471
00:18:54,718 --> 00:18:55,934
Come on, paulie,
we better get up

472
00:18:55,969 --> 00:18:57,186
some of
this furniture

473
00:18:57,221 --> 00:18:58,437
so we'll have
some protection

