our tops a little.

507
00:21:39,132 --> 00:21:40,349
Well, i
don't think

508
00:21:40,384 --> 00:21:41,600
marty's going
to hold it

509
00:21:41,635 --> 00:21:42,851
against you,
frank.

510
00:21:45,354 --> 00:21:47,856
Just like i
don't think

511
00:21:47,891 --> 00:21:50,359
bill is going
to hold all
this against us.

512
00:21:50,394 --> 00:21:52,861
We'll pay for
the damages,
bill.

513
00:21:52,896 --> 00:21:55,364
We'll take up
a collection
right away.

514
00:21:55,399 --> 00:21:58,500
We... we could
have a block party

